headline: August in Review: 12 Top Technology Press Releases
summary: With thousands of press releases published each month, it can be difficult to keep up with everything on PR Newswire. To help tech journalists and consumers stay on top of the month's most popular releases and newsworthy trends, here's a recap of some of the past month's most read- and engaged-with stories.

headline: eMed Population Health Appoints Renowned Industry Leader Amy Elkins as Chief Operating Officer
summary: eMed Population Health, Inc. today announced the appointment of Amy Elkins as Chief Operating Officer. A seasoned executive, Elkins will lead eMed's operational strategy and execution across enterprise solutions, with a focus on scaling the company's GLP-1 and preemptive care platform for employers and payers worldwide.
